            <div class="trust-row"><div class="icon-wrap"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2L4 6v6c0 5 4 9 8 10 4-1 8-5 8-10V6L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M8.5 12l2.5 2.5 4.5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div><div><strong>Your data is never sold</strong><span>One match — no spam, no lead sales.</span></div></div>
